<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1>{{title}}</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section id="form-section">
            <h2>Submit a new post</h2>
            <form id="post-form">
              <label for="post-title"></label><input type="text" id="post-title" placeholder="Post Title" required>
              <label for="post-content"></label><textarea id="post-content" placeholder="Post Content" required></textarea>
                <button type="submit">Submit</button>
            </form>
        </section>

        <section id="posts-section">
            <h2>Posts</h2>
            <ul id="posts-list"></ul>
        </section>
    </main>

    <script src="/script.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
{{! This is a simple HTML template for a blog application. It includes a form for submitting new posts and a section to display existing posts. The form uses jQuery and Axios for handling submissions and fetching posts from the server. }}